<paragraph id="8BEF369CE40AFFA0F9AB64C7FC4A377D" blockId="12.[151,1437,151,644]" pageId="12" pageNumber="13">
<emphasis id="B924EA8EE40AFFA0F9AB64C7FE54373A" bold="true" box="[197,450,511,536]" pageId="12" pageNumber="13">General distribution.</emphasis>
This species is distributed from Nova 
<collectingCountry id="F347760CE40AFFA0FA1464C7FC563735" box="[890,960,511,535]" name="United Kingdom" pageId="12" pageNumber="13">Scotia</collectingCountry>
and Quebec in 
<collectingCountry id="F347760CE40AFFA0FD1D64C7FB5C3735" box="[1139,1226,511,535]" name="Canada" pageId="12" pageNumber="13">Canada</collectingCountry>
, south through the northeastern states to Maryland and West Virginia, in Great Smoky Mountains National Park (North Carolina and Tennessee), northern 
<collectingCountry id="F347760CE40AFFA0F8E9677FFE72377D" box="[391,484,583,607]" name="Georgia" pageId="12" pageNumber="13">Georgia</collectingCountry>
, and west to Illinois, Kansas, and east Texas.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8BEF369CE40AFFA0F9AB6754FE4837A6" blockId="12.[151,1437,151,644]" box="[197,478,620,644]" pageId="12" pageNumber="13">
<emphasis id="B924EA8EE40AFFA0F9AB6754FEF637A6" bold="true" box="[197,352,620,644]" pageId="12" pageNumber="13">Larval hosts.</emphasis>
